Kids call us beggars at school.

235
00:19:00,013 --> 00:19:02,808
-How do they come down from upstairs?
-By taking the elevator.

236
00:19:10,148 --> 00:19:12,234
-Are you going downstairs?
-Yes.

237
00:19:13,652 --> 00:19:14,778
