252
00:20:25,265 --> 00:20:28,393
I'm from Unit 501.
I moved in today, so I brought rice cakes.

253
00:20:29,269 --> 00:20:30,354
Please excuse me.

254
00:20:37,861 --> 00:20:40,489
We're neighbors, so
I'll provide legal counseling for free.

255
00:20:40,572 --> 00:20:42,699
So come anytime and consult me.

256
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:45,410
Yes, that's what you should do.

